AllocateWanAddress.document: This API is used to enable public network access.
AllocateWanAddress.name: Enables public network API

ChangeReplicaToMaster.document: This API is used to promote a replica node group of a multi-AZ deployed instance to master node group or a replica node of a single-AZ deployed instance to master node.
ChangeReplicaToMaster.name: Promotes a replica node group to master node group

DescribeInstanceAccount.document: This API is used to view instance sub-account information.
DescribeInstanceAccount.name: Views instance sub-account information

DescribeInstanceMonitorBigKey.document: This API is used to query the big key of an instance.
DescribeInstanceMonitorBigKey.name: Queries the big key of an instance

DescribeInstanceMonitorBigKeySizeDist.document: This API is used to query the big key size distribution of an instance.
DescribeInstanceMonitorBigKeySizeDist.name: Queries the big key size distribution of an instance

DescribeInstanceMonitorBigKeyTypeDist.document: This API is used to query the big key type distribution of an instance
DescribeInstanceMonitorBigKeyTypeDist.name: Queries the big key type distribution of an instance

DescribeInstanceMonitorHotKey.document: This API is used to query the hot key of an instance.
DescribeInstanceMonitorHotKey.name: Queries the hot key of an instance

DescribeInstanceMonitorSIP.document: This API is used to query the access source information of an instance.
DescribeInstanceMonitorSIP.name: Queries the access source information of an instance

DescribeInstanceMonitorTookDist.document: This API is used to query the distribution of instance access duration.
DescribeInstanceMonitorTookDist.name: Queries the distribution of instance access time

DescribeInstanceMonitorTopNCmd.document: This API is used to query an instance access command.
DescribeInstanceMonitorTopNCmd.name: Queries an instance access command

DescribeInstanceMonitorTopNCmdTook.document: This API is used to query the instance CPU time.
DescribeInstanceMonitorTopNCmdTook.name: Queries the instance CPU time

DescribeInstanceNodeInfo.document: This API is used to query instance node information.
DescribeInstanceNodeInfo.name: Queries instance node information

DescribeMaintenanceWindow.document: This API is used to query instance maintenance window. The maintenance window specifies a time period during which compatible version upgrade, architecture upgrade, backend maintenance, and other operations can be performed to avoid affecting business.
DescribeMaintenanceWindow.name: Queries instance maintenance window

DescribeProductInfo.document: This API is used to query the purchasable capacity specifications of Redis instances in the specified AZ and instance type. If you are not in the allowlist for the AZ or instance type, you cannot view the details of the capacity specifications. To apply for the eligibility, please submit a ticket.
DescribeProductInfo.name: Queries the purchasable product specifications

DescribeReplicationGroup.document: This API is used to query the global replication group.
DescribeReplicationGroup.name: Queries the global replication group

DescribeSlowLog.document: This API is used to query the slow log.
DescribeSlowLog.name: Queries the slow log

InquiryPriceCreateInstance.document: This API is used to query the price for purchasing an instance.
InquiryPriceCreateInstance.name: Queries the price for purchasing an instance

InquiryPriceUpgradeInstance.document: This API is used to query the price for scaling an instance.
InquiryPriceUpgradeInstance.name: Queries the price for scaling an instance

ModfiyInstancePassword.document: This API is used to change the Redis password.
ModfiyInstancePassword.name: Changes the Redis password

ModifyInstanceReadOnly.document: This API is used to set instance input mode.
ModifyInstanceReadOnly.name: Sets instance input mode

ReleaseWanAddress.document: This API is used to disable public network access.
ReleaseWanAddress.name: Disables public network API
